{"tid":700671,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［你講我就信?］多間公司多次向DxOMark要求以金錢換取評鑑 但DxOMark未曾接受","createTime":"2018-06-13T13:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T06:24:31.000Z","uid":1714,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3f3c6559875760f9754cb9eb70521cf8e03a556c","tid":700671,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-SDUQgOsVHpM/WyEa-43EA4I/AAAAAAABip8/OWuUjgEs_awQcw3zAfpmdbvzZaU6YS01QCLcBGAs/s1600/dxomarkbanmoney.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-SDUQgOsVHpM%2FWyEa-43EA4I%2FAAAAAAABip8%2FOWuUjgEs_awQcw3zAfpmdbvzZaU6YS01QCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fdxomarkbanmoney.png&h=f722463b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/dxomarkbanmoney.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thealpha.app%2F2018%2F06%2Fdxomarkbanmoney.html&d=E53vm%2Fe9zDsGBEJNBXY9RHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c592c77b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/dxomarkbanmoney.html</a></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺最近嘅訪問入面，DxOMark市場部副主席Nicolas Touchard表示，無論係傳統相機定電話製造商，都有多間公司多次向DxOMark要求評鑑佢哋嘅產品，並以金錢作回報。但Touchard強調公司未收受過任何金錢，而特登評鑑任何產品。同時亦唔認為呢啲錢係賄賂，指「只係嗰啲公司未清楚我哋(DxOMark)嘅運作方式，尤其是嗰啲未同我哋合作過嘅，先會嘗試用錢去換評鑑。」。 </span>"},{"pid":"31259ef084c730a47f34c149551075f20b77b0c1","tid":700671,"uid":12628,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"一隻有貞節牌坊嘅雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa53a460d4b264f31e1dfa249ee31fc7dc07222","tid":700671,"uid":185693,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"DxO lab 都就黎破產 話無收錢搵鬼信。"},{"pid":"5098eeda7ea91b8dd81cf524bb97e2c5ce1de4cf","tid":700671,"uid":73731,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:3